Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.16,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde som to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:37.64,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Zbohom, Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:42.11,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj, Toa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.83,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Toa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:56.05,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:07.18,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Poďme, Gio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:10.94,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Gio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:22.74,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keď on veľmi nerozprával, ale vychádzal som sním lepšie, ako si myslíte.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:26.94,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,V skutočnosti, som ho bral, ako malého brata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:31.10,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,A teraz, som Spirytusa, zabil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.96,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,To nie je tvoja chyba.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:39.86,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Keby mi, Akira prikázala zabiť ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:44.30,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozkazy veliteľa sú absolútne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:49.00,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Bolo to rozhodnuté od momentu Rezonancie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:51.27,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som ti nerozkázala zabiť ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:55.06,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Mimochodom, prečo sa to stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.49,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo to Spirytus urobil?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.49,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola to Amagiho chyba?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:03.24,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyšetrovacie oddelenie ISDA už na tom pracuje.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:09.60,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nedalo sa nič viac urobiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:13.80,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpusť mi, Howling Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:17.69,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetko čo teraz potrebujeme urobiť...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:21.65,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,... je nájsť Kamishina Jina a Gia tak rýchlo, ako to len pôjde.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:25.51,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeme dovoliť, aby sa toto narušenie, ešte zhoršilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:31.80,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Gio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:35.45,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si išiel s Jinom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:46.72,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo? Prečo si to urobil?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:02.18,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Si si istý?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:06.99,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Či je to dobré, alebo zlé, lenže jedna z obetí bola ešte nažive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:11.05,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď som jej ukázal fotku Spirytusa, tak povedala, že si je istá.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:15.17,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Je nemysliteľné, aby sa z Komunikátora stal vrah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:17.41,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo sa to stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:20.40,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Pokračuj v pátraní.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.31,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozkaz
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:54.52,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Dopočula som, že Dragonauti zbesilo pátrajú po Kamishimovi Jinovi a Gio-vi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:57.84,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Potešilo by ma, keby tak isto pátrali aj po Album.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:01.36,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebol Kamishina Jin iba návnada?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.49,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Lenže teraz...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:07.24,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Počul si o Spirytusovi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:11.23,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Pán Kiril je toho názoru,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:14.14,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,že médiá o tom nesmú nič zistiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:15.70,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:19.90,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Máme len jedinú možnosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:22.84,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Neprichádza do úvahy, aby sa verejnosť...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.40,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,... dozvedela pravdu o D-Projekte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:31.20,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Oznámiť ľudstvu, že bolo vystavené nebezpečenstvu spôsobeným mimozemskou entitou, by mohlo vyvolať iba paniku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:36.47,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale oni už panikária, kvôli tomu incidentu z minulej noci.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.61,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebude problém, ak sa občania dozvedia,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:43.48,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,že sme s vládnym schválením tajne experimentovali s drakmi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:45.24,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je na to už prineskoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:50.62,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Veľa občanov už videlo Drgonautov jazdiacich na drakoch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:51.60,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Avšak...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:55.83,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si o tom myslíte, Komander Sakaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:59.24,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Rada by som vypočula váš názor, na túto záležitosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:03.44,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak budeme aj naďalej ukrývať identitu vraha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:06.42,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,... a potom odvracať pozornosť ľudstva od vrážd...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:11.36,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím si, že by sme malí zverejniť existenciu D-Projektu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.68,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Súhlasím.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:31.59,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Odkiaľ máš, tie šaty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:36.19,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Takto to robia ľudia, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.53,0:08:48.57,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo pre Tou znamenáš?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:52.97,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Narodil som sa, aby som Tou chránil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:54.83,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Chránil Tou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.78,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,A čo pre Tou znamenáš ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:09:00.96,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja, ja som...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:07.18,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo ja, pre ňu znamenám?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.52,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Tá pieseň...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.66,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,To je Toa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:33.23,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Počujem ju.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:38.07,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Počuješ niečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:41.12,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty ju nepočuješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:47.17,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Mesiac.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.90,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Toa je na mesiaci.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:51.03,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Mesiaci?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:10:00.60,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako to môžeš vedieť?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:03.62,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Dokážem počuť jej pieseň.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:05.65,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Pieseň?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.37,0:10:36.54,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedz, Makina...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:42.12,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,... o tom, čo sme pred tým diskutovali...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:45.50,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja by som ti nikdy neprikázala ho zabiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.60,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,V žiadnom prípade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:49.36,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:50.78,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja viem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:01.90,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:03.81,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Gio?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:04.82,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,To je on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:07.97,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Pusť ma, povedal som pusť ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:11.42,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamishina Jin a Komunikátor Gio, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:12.94,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Správne.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:17.34,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Len som ho využil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:22.31,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Zradca. Ty už nechceš vidieť Tou?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:40.04,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Zajali sme utečencov Kamishinu Jina a Komunikátora Gia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:41.66,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Opakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:46.37,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Zajali sme utečencov Kamishinu Jina a Komunikátora Gia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:47.89,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Gio!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:49.75,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Som rám aj za teba, Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:53.20,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,A to je všetko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:56.42,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže, ty hovoríš, že si počul, ako ťa Album volá..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:59.90,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,... lenže si nespomínaš na nič, čo sa stalo potom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:01.86,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:07.45,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Odveďte ho za Profesorkou Kitajimou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:08.26,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, pane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:13.23,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:20.23,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,No tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:21.93,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Vypi to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:26.60,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:29.80,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si to všetko vlastne urobil?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:32.79,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Aby som sa stretol s To-ou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:35.05,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,To je všetko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.08,0:12:39.99,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:41.20,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeš sa pohnúť?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:44.59,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, pohni tým svojím zadkom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:58.26,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo pre Tou znamenám?! Chcem zistiť, čo pre Tou znamenám.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:02.66,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ona je jediná, ktorá mi povedala, že nie som sám.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:19.58,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Narušiteľ v zóne D3.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:23.10,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozorovací monitor zaznamenal obraz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:33.21,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Gio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:35.55,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tentokrát vyviedol?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:39.30,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôže...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:43.40,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,To nie, oni to plánovali hneď od začiatku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:45.60,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira, čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:48.20,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Choď napred a zastav Gia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:49.76,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozumiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.50,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Do riti, dostal ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:00.92,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Stáť!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:04.44,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Mesiac?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:07.05,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako to môžeš vedieť?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:10.77,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Počujem jej pieseň.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.43,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Pieseň?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:19.80,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja nič nepočujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.36,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ver mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:23.02,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Toa je na mesiaci.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.43,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to pravda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:27.85,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja to viem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.85,0:14:32.40,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,A ak nebude na mesiaci?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:34.86,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak to tak nebude...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:36.85,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,... opustím ťa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.02,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, v pohode.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:46.06,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Poďme.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.70,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj chvíľku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:51.30,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Než pôjdem do vesmíru, potrebujem nejaké veci.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:53.16,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Musíme ich získať.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.85,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím otvor sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:05.54,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:10.42,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Stoj.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:17.66,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Dostal si sa dosť ďaleko, Kamishina Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:35.01,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Neutečieš.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:37.92,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,No tak, poďme naspäť.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:40.46,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám veľa otázok, ktoré sa chcem opýtať.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.66,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, nechaj ma ísť.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:47.73,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty nie si pán, takže ako chceš dokázať pilotovať draka, Gia?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.93,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemáš za sebou Rezonanciu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:51.66,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,O čo to hovoríš?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.11,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:54.40,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nehraj sa na sprostého.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:56.56,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpovedz mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:59.14,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Pán? Rezonancia?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:00.83,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,O čom to hovoríš?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:02.28,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedala som ti, aby si sa nehral na blbca.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:06.21,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja sa nehrám! Ja neviem odpovedať, lebo nerozumiem ničomu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:08.14,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to všetko je?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:10.03,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,O čo tu ide?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.18,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Iba to chcem vedieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.74,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedz mi to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:17.71,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,On vážne nič nevie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:20.72,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak, aký je potom vzťah medzi ním a Giom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:39.03,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem zistiť pravdu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:40.62,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže preto idem za To-ou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.78,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem ju vidieť, a zistiť to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:55.00,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Stoj!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:26.16,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Neutečieš mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:35.63,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Mal by si mať Rezonanciu s Kazukim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:38.27,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak prečo Kazukiho nepočúvaš?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:39.86,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja nie som nikoho.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:41.65,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebudem nikoho počúvať.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:43.72,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si slobodný?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:44.87,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto vie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:52.92,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Zistila som, že si zaujímavý.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.12,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Vôbec ma nezaujímaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:15.01,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Makina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:10.43,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem zistiť pravdu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:13.71,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže preto idem za To-ou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:17.37,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Neprenasleduj ich.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:20.88,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,On to možno zmení.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:22.78,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Zmení čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:28.30,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Vzťahy medzi drakmi a ľuďmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:34.32,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Aktualizér potvrdil signál G-10 vo vzdušnom priestore nad Novou Ogasawarou.
